data.description: Large double lot! This adorable bungalow is just ready for your touch. The bathroom has been newly renovated. This is a chance to own a home with a two-car garage and office inside. A guy can work on his vehicles, start a home-based business, or create the man caves of your dreams. She shed is also on site. Raised garden beds are also a plus. Plant your garlic now for spring harvest.
